    <h1>Post Office Schemes vs Bank FDs: The Complete 2026 Comparison</h1>
    <div class="article-dateline">
      <span class="article-dateline__item"><span class="article-dateline__label">Published:</span> 20 January 2026</span>
      <span class="article-dateline__sep">·</span>
      <span class="article-dateline__item">{% set author = authors[authorId] %}By <a href="{{ author.url }}">{{ author.name }}</a>, {{ author.credentials }}</span>
    </div>
    <p class="blog-article__intro">The post office feels old-fashioned. Queues, paper forms, passbooks. But India Post's small savings schemes offer government-guaranteed returns that consistently beat major bank FDs — sometimes by a full percentage point. If you're parking money for safety and income, the post office deserves a serious look.</p>

